repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The records consist of subject files of the associate university librarian documenting the growth and development of the Yale University Library's holdings, with a focus on the bibliography department.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 32-B (YRG 32-B), Records of deputy, associate, and assistant university librarians of Yale University.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the records is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Associate University Librarian for Collection development, Yale University (RU 124). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by accession

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of subject files of the associate university librarian documenting the growth and development of the Yale University Library's holdings, with a focus on the bibliography department.
